{"tid":1595923,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我感覺到, 我能力強左好多","createTime":"2019-09-26T09:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T05:28:05.000Z","uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6b033b6da387223272b9a34a4674f39e3bceae47","tid":1595923,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"呢幾日, 我感覺到自己要食好多野, <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日都覺得好肚餓,<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲食物好快消化, <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要飲好多水,<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屙既尿多左, <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔駛點做運動個肚腩都瘦左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飲左既水可以完全感覺到佢流去腎臟再排返出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屎就完全係得番消化唔到既纖維同少量水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n訓又訓少左都好精神, <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全身都充滿能量咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係咪己經可以同識得爆氣既修道船一戰呢???????<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73c6a45e8ce40c469f802d1c235bedb6d293da5","tid":1595923,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:27:26.000Z","msg":"秋天食慾旺盛好正常"},{"pid":"704be8945b3a09da978b6911cfa9d3b29851bebc","tid":1595923,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e73c6a45e8ce40c469f802d1c235bedb6d293da5","tid":1595923,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:27:26.000Z","msg":"秋天食慾旺盛好正常"},"cit